                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西风剑术 · 白"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">阳华</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/4c999a92de43cfba640c30b45c782fc9_6288048578116106041.png",
                "id": "talent18167",
                "key": "创生法 · 拟造阳华",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "创生法 · 拟造阳华"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">阳华</span>在场，就使此伤害+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/42d2ae5af0169e6938febe18de57d31a_4317077883258125697.png",
                "id": "talent33463",
                "key": "诞生式 · 大地之潮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "诞生式 · 大地之潮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场时：</span>我方角色进行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">下落攻击</span>时少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无色元素</span>。（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2400986943641716340.png",
                "id": "talent31026",
                "key": "阳华",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/02297af9d3309f3e4e40eca8911a19f6_7069797293172672856.png",
                "title": "阳华"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_4516396808357117820.png",
                "id": "talent22280",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">下落攻击</span></strong></p><p>角色被切换为「出战角色」后，本回合内的下一个战斗行动若为「普通攻击」，则被被视为「下落攻击」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">无色元素</span></strong></p><p>可以用任意类型的元素骰子组合，来支付此类费用。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3794533788443591664.png",
                "id": "talent76833",
                "key": "规则术语",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "规则术语"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
